#. Tag: title
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<command>kded5</command> can be configured with the <filename>kded5rc</"
#| "filename> ini-style configuration file. On Unix systems, this can be "
#| "found at <filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded5rc</"
#| "filename>; if <varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> is not set, this "
#| "defaults to <filename>~/.config/kded5rc</filename>."
msgid ""
"<command>kded6</command> can be configured with the <filename>kded5rc</"
"filename> ini-style configuration file. On &UNIX; systems, this can be found "
"at <filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded5rc</filename>; if "
"<varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> is not set, this defaults to "
"<filename>~/.config/kded5rc</filename>."
msgstr ""
"<command>kded5</command> saab seadistada <filename>kded5rc</filename> ini-"
"stiilis seadistusfailiga. Unixi süsteemides leiab selle asukohast "
"<filename><varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname>/kded5rc</filename>; kui "
"<varname>$XDG_CONFIG_HOME</varname> ei ole määratud, on selleks vaikimisi "
"<filename>~/.config/kded5rc</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Configuration file entries are read on-demand, so changes can be made "
#| "while <command>kded5</command> is running. However, all the current "
#| "configuration options only really affect the startup behaviour of "
#| "<command>kded5</command>."
msgid ""
"Configuration file entries are read on-demand, so changes can be made while "
"<command>kded6</command> is running. However, all the current configuration "
"options only really affect the startup behaviour of <command>kded6</command>."
msgstr ""
"Seadistusfaili kirjeid loetakse vajaduse korral, nii et sellesse võib "
"muudatusi teha ka siis, kui <command>kded5</command> töötab. Ent kõik "
"praegused seadistusvalikud puudutavad tegelikult ainult <command>kded5</"
"command> käivitumisaegset käitumist."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <option>[General]</option> section has the following options:"
msgstr "Sektsioonis <option>[General]</option> on järgmised valikud:"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckSycoca"
msgstr "CheckSycoca"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to update sycoca at startup (default: <constant>true</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"Kas uuendada sycoca't käivitamisel (vaikimisi <constant>true</constant>)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckUpdates"
msgstr "CheckUpdates"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to perform outstanding KConfig updates at startup (default: "
"<constant>true</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"Kas sooritada ootel KConfigi uuendused käivitamisel (vaikimisi "
"<constant>true</constant>)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "CheckFileStamps"
msgstr "CheckFileStamps"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:107
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Whether to check file timestamps when performing the initial sycoca "
#| "update (default: <constant>true</constant>). See the documentation for "
#| "<command>kbuildsycoca5</command> for more details."
msgid ""
"Whether to check file timestamps when performing the initial sycoca update "
"(default: <constant>true</constant>). See the documentation for "
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> for more details."
msgstr ""
"Kas kontrollida algse sycoca uuendamise ajal faili ajatemplit (vaikimisi "
"<constant>true</constant>). Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest "
"<command>kbuildsycoca5</command> dokumentatsioon."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "DelayedCheck"
msgstr "DelayedCheck"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to delay the initial sycoca update until about a minute after "
"starting (default: <constant>false</constant>)."
msgstr ""
"Kas lükata algne sycoca uuendamine käivitamisel umbes minuti võrra edasi "
"(vaikimisi <constant>false</constant>)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kded6.8.docbook:118
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Each module also has a <option>[Module-<replaceable>name</replaceable>]</"
#| "option> section in <filename>kded5rc</filename>, where <replaceable>name</"
#| "replaceable> is the name of the module's desktop file without the "
#| "<filename>.desktop</filename> extension. This contains an "
#| "<option>autoload</option> option that specifies whether the module should "
#| "be automatically loaded when <command>kded5</command> is started "
#| "(default: <constant>false</constant>). Note that this setting can also be "
#| "changed via <command>kded5</command>'s D-Bus interface."
msgid ""
"Each module also has a <option>[Module-<replaceable>name</replaceable>]</"
"option> section in <filename>kded5rc</filename>, where <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable> is the name of the module's desktop file without the <filename>."
"desktop</filename> extension. This contains an <option>autoload</option> "
"option that specifies whether the module should be automatically loaded when "
"<command>kded6</command> is started (default: <constant>false</constant>). "
"Note that this setting can also be changed via <command>kded6</command>'s "
"&DBus; interface."
msgstr ""
"Igal moodulil on failis <filename>kded5rc</filename> oma <option>[Module-"
"<replaceable>nimi</replaceable>]</option> sektsioon, mille puhul "
"<replaceable>nimi</replaceable> tähendab siin mooduli töölauafaili nime ilma "
"laiendita <filename>.desktop</filename>. See sisaldab valikut "
"<option>autoload</option>, mis määrab, kas moodul tuleb automaatselt "
"laadida, kui <command>kded5</command> käivitub (vaikimisi <constant>false</"
"constant>). Pane tähele, et seda seadistust saab muuta ka <command>kded5</"
"command> D-Busi liidese kaudu."

